---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <Header />
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-black">
    <section class="relative h-screen w-full overflow-hidden bg-black" style="height: 100dvh;">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-10" style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 40%, rgba(191,238,255,.08), transparent 40%), #050505;"></div>
      <div class="hero-scrim absolute inset-0 z-40 pointer-events-none" style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,.42), rgba(0,0,0,.12) 42%, rgba(0,0,0,.02) 72%, rgba(0,0,0,.28) 100%);"></div>

      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-50 flex items-end px-5 pb-10 pt-28 sm:px-8 sm:pb-12 md:px-12 lg:pb-14 pointer-events-none">
        <div class="w-full">
          <div class="flex flex-col justify-end gap-5 lg:max-w-[720px] min-h-0">
            <div class="hero-anim hero-fade flex items-center gap-3 text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[.24em] text-white/80" style="animation-delay:.18s;"><span class="h-px w-14 bg-[#bfeeff]"></span>Relations Publiques</div>
            <h1 class="text-white leading-[.88] drop-shadow-[0_4px_28px_rgba(0,0,0,.85)]">
              <span class="hero-anim hero-reveal-text block text-5xl font-medium sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-[6.6rem]" style="letter-spacing:-.08em;animation-delay:.25s;">Faites parler</span>
              <span class="hero-anim hero-reveal-text -mt-1 block font-playfair text-5xl italic sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-[6.6rem]" style="letter-spacing:-.06em;animation-delay:.42s;">de vous. Vraiment.</span>
            </h1>
            <div class="hero-anim hero-fade max-w-[560px]" style="animation-delay:.68s;">
              <p class="max-w-[500px] text-sm leading-relaxed text-white drop-shadow-[0_3px_22px_rgba(0,0,0,.95)] sm:text-base md:text-lg">Les RP accessibles aux independants et PME du Canton de Vaud. Des 80 CHF, sans contrat annuel.</p>
              <div class="mt-5 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
                <a href="#services" class="pointer-events-auto w-fit rounded-full bg-white px-7 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-black transition-all hover:scale-[1.03] hover:bg-[#effbff] hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-[#bfeeff]/25 active:scale-95">Decouvrir les services</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="pointer-events-auto w-fit rounded-full border border-white/30 bg-transparent px-7 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white backdrop-blur transition-all hover:border-white/55 hover:bg-white/10 active:scale-95">Me contacter</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="vertical-label hero-anim hero-fade absolute left-4 bottom-10 z-50 hidden text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[.26em] text-white/50 md:block pointer-events-none" style="animation-delay:.95s;">ORIANE ANNEN · RP 2.0</div>
    </section>

    <div class="site-bg text-white">
      <div class="content-layer">
        <section id="services" class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-28 sm:px-8 md:py-40">
          <p class="eyebrow reveal"><span class="eyebrow-line"></span> Mes services</p>
          <h2 class="reveal mt-7 text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl" style="letter-spacing:-.055em;">Des RP concues <span class="font-playfair italic">pour vous</span></h2>

          <div class="mt-14 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
            <article class="reveal stagger glass-card rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 p-6 md:p-8">
              <h3 class="font-playfair text-3xl italic">Relations presse</h3>
              <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/65">Communiques, dossiers de presse, relations avec les journalistes romands, placement presse, radio, TV et podcasts. Vos posts vous rendent visible. Un article vous rend credible.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="reveal stagger glass-card rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 p-6 md:p-8 md:translate-y-10">
              <h3 class="font-playfair text-3xl italic">Preparation aux medias</h3>
              <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/65">Kit media complet, messages cles, cadre juridique de vos prises de parole, accompagnement quand un media vous approche.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="reveal stagger glass-card rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 p-6 md:p-8">
              <h3 class="font-playfair text-3xl italic">Communication digitale</h3>
              <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/65">Gestion des reseaux sociaux, strategie digitale sur mesure, contenus qui vous ressemblent. Etre partout ne sert a rien. Etre au bon endroit change tout.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>

        <div class="section-line mx-auto h-px max-w-6xl"></div>

        <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-28 sm:px-8 md:py-40">
          <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[.95fr_1.05fr] lg:items-center">
            <div>
              <p class="eyebrow reveal"><span class="eyebrow-line"></span> Pourquoi les RP ?</p>
              <h2 class="reveal mt-8 max-w-4xl text-4xl font-medium leading-[1.02] tracking-tight sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-[4.6rem]" style="letter-spacing:-.055em;">
                <span class="text-mask"><span>Les reseaux vous rendent visible.</span></span>
                <span class="text-mask"><span>La pub vous rend connu.</span></span>
                <span class="text-mask font-playfair italic text-white/90"><span>Les medias vous rendent credible.</span></span>
              </h2>
            </div>
            <div class="reveal glass-card rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 p-6 sm:p-8">
              <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-white/65 md:text-lg">Quand un journal, une radio ou un podcast parle de vous, tout change : ce n'est plus vous qui dites que vous etes bon — c'est un tiers de confiance. Et ce jour-la, ce sont vos clients qui viennent a vous.</p>
              <div class="mt-8 space-y-4 border-t border-white/10 pt-6">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[.24em] text-white/40">Le probleme</p>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-white/60">Les agences RP facturent plusieurs milliers de francs par mois. Hors de portee d'une PME.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[.24em] text-exo-cyan">Ma reponse</p>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Des 80 CHF</p>
                  <p class="text-sm text-white/60">Sans contrat annuel. Sans budget d'agence.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <div class="section-line mx-auto h-px max-w-6xl"></div>

        <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-28 sm:px-8 md:py-40">
          <p class="eyebrow reveal"><span class="eyebrow-line"></span> Tarifs</p>
          <h2 class="reveal mt-6 text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl" style="letter-spacing:-.055em;">Formules <span class="font-playfair italic">adaptees</span></h2>

          <div class="mt-14 space-y-4">
            <div class="reveal glass-card rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 p-7 md:p-9">
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-6">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[.26em] text-exo-cyan">Ponctuel</p>
                  <h3 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight">Service Flash</h3>
                  <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/55">Redaction et diffusion d'un communique de presse, contact journalistes, conseil cible ou gestion de crise. Une reponse rapide et professionnelle.</p>
                </div>
                <span class="shrink-0 font-playfair text-3xl italic text-exo-cyan">80 CHF</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="reveal glass-card rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 p-7 md:p-9">
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-6">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[.26em] text-exo-cyan">Abonnement</p>
                  <h3 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight">Relations Publiques au mois</h3>
                  <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/55">Chaque mois : recherche d'angles, redaction de communiques, demarchage medias. Possibilite d'inclure la gestion des reseaux sociaux.</p>
                </div>
                <span class="shrink-0 font-playfair text-3xl italic text-exo-cyan">250 CHF/mois</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="reveal glass-card rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 p-7 md:p-9">
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-6">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[.26em] text-exo-cyan">Sur-mesure</p>
                  <h3 class="mt-2 text-3xl font-medium tracking-tight">Campagne de A a Z</h3>
                  <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/55">Strategie complete : analyse, messages, planification, suivi des retombees. Exemple : lancement de food truck avec communique, partenaires locaux et journee degustation presse.</p>
                </div>
                <span class="shrink-0 font-playfair text-3xl italic text-white/55">Sur devis</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <div class="section-line mx-auto h-px max-w-6xl"></div>

        <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-28 sm:px-8 md:py-40">
          <p class="eyebrow reveal"><span class="eyebrow-line"></span> A propos</p>
          <div class="reveal mt-7 glass-card rounded-[2rem] border border-white/10 p-7 md:p-10">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-5xl" style="letter-spacing:-.055em;">Diplomee d'un Brevet federal <span class="font-playfair italic">en relations publiques</span></h2>
            <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-base leading-relaxed text-white/65 md:text-lg">Je me suis specialisee dans l'accompagnement des petites entreprises, bars, restaurants et commerces locaux. Aujourd'hui en formation en marketing digital pour une approche 360° de la communication. Formee par le Dr Philippe Amez-Droz, specialiste en sciences de la communication a l'Universite de Geneve.</p>
            <blockquote class="mt-8 border-l-2 border-exo-cyan pl-6 font-playfair text-xl italic text-white/80 md:text-2xl">« J'aime commencer un projet, une discussion ou un simple mail avec le sourire aux levres. »</blockquote>
          </div>
        </section>

        <div class="section-line mx-auto h-px max-w-6xl"></div>

        <section id="faq" class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-24 sm:px-8 md:py-32">
          <p class="eyebrow reveal"><span class="eyebrow-line"></span> FAQ</p>
          <h2 class="reveal mt-7 text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl" style="letter-spacing:-.055em;">Questions <span class="font-playfair italic">frequentes</span></h2>
          <div class="mt-12 divide-y divide-white/10 border-y border-white/10">
            <div class="faq-item reveal"><button class="faq-toggle flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-6 py-7 text-left" type="button"><span class="text-lg font-medium tracking-tight">Que faites-vous en relations publiques ?</span><iconify-icon icon="solar:add-circle-linear" width="24" class="faq-icon shrink-0 text-exo-cyan"></iconify-icon></button><div class="faq-body"><p class="pb-7 pr-10 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/60">Je connecte votre entreprise aux bons medias et journalistes. Je valorise votre image, gere vos communications, redige vos contenus presse.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-item reveal"><button class="faq-toggle flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-6 py-7 text-left" type="button"><span class="text-lg font-medium tracking-tight">Comment se deroule une collaboration ?</span><iconify-icon icon="solar:add-circle-linear" width="24" class="faq-icon shrink-0 text-exo-cyan"></iconify-icon></button><div class="faq-body"><p class="pb-7 pr-10 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/60">On echang d'abord sur vos objectifs. Je construis ensuite une strategie personnalisee : messages cles, ciblage medias, opportunites, calendrier et suivi.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-item reveal"><button class="faq-toggle flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-6 py-7 text-left" type="button"><span class="text-lg font-medium tracking-tight">Quels types d'entreprises accompagnez-vous ?</span><iconify-icon icon="solar:add-circle-linear" width="24" class="faq-icon shrink-0 text-exo-cyan"></iconify-icon></button><div class="faq-body"><p class="pb-7 pr-10 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/60">Toutes les structures avec une histoire authentique a raconter : PME, associations, independants, commerces locaux. L'important est l'humain et la coherence.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-item reveal"><button class="faq-toggle flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-6 py-7 text-left" type="button"><span class="text-lg font-medium tracking-tight">Aidez-vous aussi avec les reseaux sociaux ?</span><iconify-icon icon="solar:add-circle-linear" width="24" class="faq-icon shrink-0 text-exo-cyan"></iconify-icon></button><div class="faq-body"><p class="pb-7 pr-10 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/60">Oui. Grace a ma formation en marketing digital, j'integre les social media dans une vision 360° : contenu coherent, posture, lignes editoriales et gestion responsable.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-item reveal"><button class="faq-toggle flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-6 py-7 text-left" type="button"><span class="text-lg font-medium tracking-tight">Comment gerez-vous les crises ?</span><iconify-icon icon="solar:add-circle-linear" width="24" class="faq-icon shrink-0 text-exo-cyan"></iconify-icon></button><div class="faq-body"><p class="pb-7 pr-10 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/60">Avec calme, methode et transparence. Je vous aide a formuler les bons messages et proteger votre reputation aupres du public et des medias.</p></div></div>
            <div class="faq-item reveal"><button class="faq-toggle flex w-full items-center justify-between gap-6 py-7 text-left" type="button"><span class="text-lg font-medium tracking-tight">Travaillez-vous directement avec les journalistes ?</span><iconify-icon icon="solar:add-circle-linear" width="24" class="faq-icon shrink-0 text-exo-cyan"></iconify-icon></button><div class="faq-body"><p class="pb-7 pr-10 text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/60">Oui. Je cible les medias pertinents, cree des opportunites avec les journalistes, redige vos communiques et maximise vos chances d'etre publie.</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <div class="section-line mx-auto h-px max-w-6xl"></div>

        <section id="contact" class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-5 py-28 sm:px-8 md:py-40">
          <div class="reveal soft-panel relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2.4rem] border border-white/10 px-7 py-16 text-center shadow-[0_40px_120px_rgba(0,0,0,.55)] sm:px-12 md:py-28">
            <div class="absolute inset-x-10 top-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#bfeeff]/60 to-transparent"></div>
            <p class="text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[.26em] text-exo-cyan">Contact</p>
            <h2 class="mx-auto mt-7 max-w-4xl text-4xl font-medium leading-[1.02] tracking-tight sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl" style="letter-spacing:-.06em;">Et si on <span class="font-playfair italic">echangeait</span> ?</h2>
            <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-white/60">Discutons de vos objectifs sans engagement.</p>
            <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row">
              <a href="mailto:oriane.annen03@gmail.com" class="w-fit rounded-full bg-white px-8 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-black transition-all hover:scale-[1.03] hover:bg-[#effbff] hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-[#bfeeff]/25 active:scale-95">Envoyer un email</a>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-10 text-sm text-white/40">
              <p>Oriane Annen · Vy d'Echallens 1M, 1004 Lausanne, Suisse</p>
              <p class="mt-1">oriane.annen03@gmail.com</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <Footer />
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
